        "work_pbt_desc": "Neco, ge\u00e7mi\u015finden ka\u00e7mak i\u00e7in bat\u0131ya g\u00f6\u00e7 eder. Ger\u00e7ek an\u0131 geldi\u011finde, yaratt\u0131\u011f\u0131 ger\u00e7ekli\u011fin sadece bir fanteziden ibaret oldu\u011funu ve ger\u00e7ekten \u00e7ok uzak oldu\u011funu fark eder. Ger\u00e7e\u011fi kavramak i\u00e7in kendi i\u00e7ine bakar.",
        "work_pbt_short": "Alg\u0131 Ger\u00e7e\u011fi G\u00f6md\u00fc",
